# VROOM Engine Standards

## Coordinate Standard
All spatial data MUST be represented as `[Longitude, Latitude]` to conform with GeoJSON and VROOM specifications.

## Corporate Environment
For REST API calls, the system operates in a corporate IT environment. You must disable urllib3 warnings and set `verify=False`:
```python
import urllib3
urllib3.disable_warnings(urllib3.exceptions.InsecureRequestWarning)
# requests.get(url, verify=False)
```

## Temporal Precision
All routing logic MUST mathematically account for departure time.
Leverage TomTom's time-dependent traffic multipliers in travel estimations so that routes generated correctly reflect dynamic real-time conditions.
